body:
Using lombok 1.18.16 did not work for me. I added the argument below in the build process VM options in
Setting:-
Build, Execution, Deployment -> Compiler -> Shared build process VM
options
and it worked
https://github.com/rzwitserloot/lombok/issues/2592
Better solution than the accepted one since you don't have to modify your project files.
Worked also for me without changing dependencies... Thank you!
Should have been the accepted answer I think.
